Every spell has additional specific information in ~/mages/help/.
Each spell belongs to a single school or to the universal category.  
Univeral spells are gained along with guild levels and are basically guild commands.
Learned spells belong to one of the eight schools of magic, listed with their abbrevations:

abju [Abjuration]  conj [Conjuration]  ench [Enchantment]  evoc [Evocation]
divi [Divination]  illu [Illusion]     necr [Necromancy]   tran [Transmutation]

LVL SPELL               SCHOOL COMMAND    COST TIME   COMP       EFFECTS
--- ------------------- ------ -------    ---- ---- ------------ ----------------------------------------------
 1  Augury               divi  augury      30   --   ----------  gives relative info on monster strength   
 1  Color-Spray          illu  cspray      27   --   ----------  10+r(21) other|light dmg      
 1  Continual Flame      evoc  cflame      40   --   any object  surrounds object with fire, giving off light
 1  Darkvision           tran  darkvis     30   --   ----------  dark_sight object - limited time
 1  Death Knell          necr  dknell     spec  --   ----------  finish move, costs 1/3 of AHP in sps   
 1  Detect Alignment     divi  detect      20   --   ----------  relative alignment
 1  Emote                illu  emote        2   --   ----------  colorized emote
 1  Erase                tran  erase       15   --   ----------  ability to erase arcane mark, wizard mark, or glyphs
 1  Faerie Fire          evoc  ffire       25   --   ----------  reduces opponent's AC
 1  Heal Light Wounds    conj  lheal       30   --   ----------  heal hps 20+r(21)
 1  Magic Missle         evoc  mssle       27   --   ----------  5+r(31) magical dmg, up to 5 missles based on evoc stat
 1  Unseen Servant       conj  userv       35    1   ----------  sell to shop remotely

