 2  Alarm                abju  alarm       40   --   ----------  notifies when anyone enters room - only 1 at time
 2  Chromatic Orb        evoc  orb         34   --   ----------  r(51) other|light dmg
 2  Death Watch          necr  dwatch     spec  --   ----------  % of hps for all in room, costs 15 sps per target
 2  Enchant Weapon       ench  enchant     200  --   any weapon  gives +1 WC bonus to a weapon, only cast once on item
 2  Instant Summons      conj  isummon     50   --   wep w/mark  teleports any item that has player's arcane mark to them 
 2  Sigil                abju  sigil       50    4   amber rod   summons monster to protect kill (see ~NPC/sigil_mon.c)
