 3  Entangle             tran  entangle   spec   3   venus ess.  lowers opponent's AC, costs 3*reduction*round (see ~OBJ/entangle_obj.c) 
 3  Fireball             evoc  fball       10   --   ----------  10+r(41) other|fire dmg
 3  Khirstel             conj  khirstel    65   10   ----------  summons Khirstel pet (see ~OBJ/khirstel.c)
 3  Telekensis           tran  telek       40    5   ----------  transport item to another player
 3  Wizard Mark          illu  wmark       30    3   ----------  leave a message on the ground

