 4  Glyph of Warding     abju  glyph
 4  Poison Bolt          evoc  pbolt       55   --   ----------  10+r(21) other|poison dmg + 3 rounds 3+r(8) other|poison dmg
 4  Ray of Frost         evoc  rfrost      48   --   ----------  10+r(51) other|ice dmg
 4  Regenerate           tran  regen       
